markdownRemark.html: Almost to the end. I would’be liked more pain for Sugou, the despicable Game Master. It ended too quickly, I was hoping that once Kirito lowered the pain observer setting he would suffer more. Even after being cut in half, he was still conscious and not dying of the pain.
